<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>We May Still Be Able to Help</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #d9534f;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>We’re currently filing returns for thousands of clients, and if you
            haven’t completed your filing yet, there’s a chance we’ll need to
            file an extension first.</p>
          <p>The closer we get to the deadline, the harder it becomes to ensure
            everything is submitted on time, which can lead to penalties and
            compliance issues.</p>
          <p>Even if you’re not ready to file, we can still help protect you.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call us now at
            <a
              href="tel:{{number}}"
              style="color: #d9534f; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{number}}</a>
            today. This cannot wait any longer.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>